categories: Category:Unidentified Jedi of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: In 33 BBY, a Rodian Jedi helped defend the Coruscant Jedi Temple when it was raided by the Yinchorri. While the Jedi were successful in repelling the invaders, Jedi Knight Tieren Nie-Tan was slain. This Jedi was among those mourning his death.
